    "caption": "Muddy, patient, and absolutely not to be underestimated.",
    "shortDescription": "Water buffalo are among the strongest domestic animals on Earth — farmers in Asia and Africa have worked alongside them for thousands of years to plow fields and haul heavy loads. They love nothing more than a good wallow in a cool muddy pool, which keeps their skin from drying out in the heat. Fun fact: Water buffalo horns can span up to two meters from tip to tip."
